@startuml
title UC10 查看预约统计报表 时序图

actor Admin as A
boundary ReportPage as B
control ReportController as C
participant ReportService as RS
participant ReservationService as RES
participant RoomService as RMS

A -> B: 选择时间范围、校区、房间类型\n点击“生成报表”
B -> C: queryReport(criteria)

C -> RS: generateReport(criteria)

RS -> RES: queryReservations(criteria)
RES --> RS: reservations

RS -> RMS: queryRooms(criteria)
RMS --> RS: rooms

RS -> RS: 统计计算\n(使用率、违约率、平均时长等)
RS --> C: ReportResult

C --> B: showReport(result)
B --> A: 展示统计报表

@enduml
